  <brief_title>The Role of Serum Anticholinergic Activity in ACVB Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Serum Anticholinergic Activity (SAA) and BIS-EEG as Potential Markers for Cognitive Ability and/or the Anticholinergic Medication in ACVB Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
